## Pacotes


::: {.cell hash='software-version_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-2_e488b73742f08e6215687a01dfeaf27b'}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(dplyr)
library(DT)
library(fs)
library(getLattes) 
library(janitor) 
library(lubridate) 
library(purrr) 
library(rio)
library(tibble)
library(tictoc) 
library(tidyr)
library(xml2)

devtools::session_info()$packages |> 
  as.data.frame() |> 
  dplyr::filter(attached == TRUE) |> 
  dplyr::select(loadedversion, date) |> 
  tibble::rownames_to_column(var = "package_name") |>
  knitr::kable(booktabs = T, align = "l") 
```

## Softwares externos


::: {.cell hash='software-version_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-3_c6e60b2c7c6e1ef73c32260df77e89e9'}

```{.r .cell-code}
sessioninfo::session_info(info = "external") |>
  unlist() |>
  as.data.frame() |>
  tibble::rownames_to_column() |>
  setNames(c('external_software', 'version')) |>
  dplyr::mutate(external_software = gsub('external.', '', external_software)) |>
  knitr::kable(booktabs = T, align = "l")
```
